'''ᱫᱟᱱᱟᱯᱩᱨ''' (ᱵᱟᱝᱢᱟ ᱫᱤᱱᱟᱯᱩᱨ ᱱᱤᱡᱟᱹᱢᱚᱛ ᱟᱨᱵᱟᱝ ᱫᱤᱱᱟᱯᱩᱨ ᱧᱩᱛᱩᱢ ᱛᱮᱦᱚᱸ ᱵᱟᱰᱟᱭᱚᱜᱼᱟ) [[ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ]] ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ [[ᱵᱤᱦᱟᱨ]] ᱯᱚᱱᱚᱛ ᱨᱮ [[ᱯᱟᱴᱱᱟ]] ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱩᱯᱥᱚᱦᱚᱨ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref name="autogenerated1">[http://urban.bih.nic.in/Docs/CDP/CDP-Danapur.pdf City Development Plan for Danapur] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305210720/http://urban.bih.nic.in/Docs/CDP/CDP-Danapur.pdf |date=5 March 2014 }} 2014-03-05</ref> ᱒᱐᱑᱑ ᱨᱤᱱ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱮᱞ ᱑᱘᱒,᱒᱔᱑ ᱦᱚᱲ ᱠᱚ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱯᱟᱴᱱᱟ ᱢᱟᱦᱟᱱᱚᱜᱚᱨ ᱴᱚᱴᱷᱟ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱴᱷᱟᱶ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾<ref name="census1">{{cite web |url=http://www.census2011.co.in/census/city/175-dinapur-nizamat.html |title=Dinapur Nizamat City Population Census 2011 &#124; Bihar |publisher=Census2011.co.in |accessdate=2014-03-05 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305212700/http://www.census2011.co.in/census/city/175-dinapur-nizamat.html |archivedate=5 March 2014 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱴᱷᱟᱯᱚᱱ ᱑᱘᱘᱗ ᱨᱮ ᱱᱟᱜᱟᱨᱯᱟᱞᱤᱠᱟ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱣ ᱞᱮᱱᱟ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AE_LIg9G5CgC&pg=PA11&dq=danapur&hl=en&sa=X&ei=0-JqT9rwGIbIrQe605mhAg&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=danapur&f=false |title=Students' Britannica India&nbsp;— Google Books |publisher=Books.google.co.in |date= |accessdate=2014-03-05}}</ref> ᱫᱟᱱᱟᱯᱩᱨ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱥᱟᱭᱵᱮᱨᱤᱭᱟᱱ ᱠᱨᱮᱱ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱛᱮ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱟᱥᱨᱟᱭ ᱟᱨ ᱦᱮᱭᱪᱟᱨᱤ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ, ᱟᱫᱚ ᱞᱚᱠᱟᱞ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ''ᱡᱟᱱᱜᱤᱞ'' ᱠᱚ ᱢᱮᱛᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱠᱚ ᱾ ᱱᱤᱭᱟᱹ ᱡᱚᱛᱚ ᱥᱮᱨᱢᱟ ᱡᱟᱯᱩᱫ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱫᱟᱜ ᱨᱮ ᱯᱨᱟᱠᱨᱤᱛᱤᱠ ᱞᱟᱹᱜᱤᱫ ᱥᱮᱱᱚᱜ ᱟᱠᱚ ᱟᱨ ᱨᱟᱵᱟᱝ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱫᱟᱜ ᱮᱛᱚᱦᱚᱵ ᱢᱟᱬᱟᱝ ᱱᱚᱣᱟ ᱴᱷᱟᱶ ᱫᱚ ᱟᱲᱟᱜ ᱜᱤᱰᱤ ᱠᱟᱜ ᱟ ᱠᱚ ᱾ ᱵᱤᱦᱟᱨ ᱟᱨ ᱡᱷᱟᱨᱠᱷᱚᱸᱰ ᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱩᱯᱼᱴᱚᱴᱷᱟ ᱦᱮᱰᱠᱩᱣᱟᱴᱚᱨ ᱱᱚᱰᱮ ᱨᱤᱱ ᱥᱤᱯᱟᱹᱦᱤ ᱪᱷᱟᱵᱽᱱᱤ ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱠᱚᱣᱟ ᱾ <ref>{{cite web |author=Ramashankar |url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1101208/jsp/bihar/story_13271306.jsp |title=The Telegraph&nbsp;— Calcutta (Kolkata) &#124; Bihar &#124; Police force to hire 9000 ex-armymen |publisher=Telegraphindia.com |date=2010-12-08 |accessdate=2014-03-05 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221151150/http://www.telegraphindia.com/1101208/jsp/bihar/story_13271306.jsp |archivedate=21 February 2015 |df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/New-commander-of-Danapur-Army-HQ/articleshow/4475821.cms?referral=PM |title=New commander of Danapur Army HQ&nbsp;— The Times of India |publisher=Timesofindia.indiatimes.com |date=2009-05-03 |accessdate=2014-03-05 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201210156/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/patna/New-commander-of-Danapur-Army-HQ/articleshow/4475821.cms?referral=PM |archivedate=1 December 2017 |df=dmy-all }}</ref> 
